  "prd_section": "16",
  "_comment": [
    "Canonical row-to-test manifest for the PRD §16 edge-case contract (issue #164).",
    "The S32 integration gate's §16 scenario (tools/integration/run_all.sh) reads THIS file",
    "and executes every mapped test explicitly, failing if any canonical §16 row is absent,",
    "any mapped test is renamed/removed (zero -list matches), or any mapped test is skipped.",
    "",
    "Every row's `edge_case` MUST match a PRD §16 table row VERBATIM; the gate cross-checks",
    "this manifest against docs/PRD.md §16 and fails on any unclassified or stale row.",
    "",
    "classification:",
    "  go_gate         — offline-testable in the Go core; this gate runs `go test` for each",
    "                    listed {package,name} against the compose Postgres and requires PASS.",
    "  other_scenario  — offline-testable, but executed by ANOTHER run_all.sh scenario in the",
    "                    SAME `task test:integration` invocation (named in `scenario`); the gate",
    "                    asserts that scenario is still wired.",
    "  other_plane     — offline-testable in a NON-Go plane whose automated suite runs in a",
    "                    different CI job (e.g. the `ts` job); the gate asserts each referenced",
    "                    {file,marker} still exists so a rename cannot silently drop coverage.",
    "  non_automatable — NOT offline-reproducible yet (needs a live/paid dependency or an unbuilt",
    "                    fixture); MUST carry an `owner` and a `reason`. Reported, never executed."
  ],
